msgid ""
"Matriarchs of Emptiness own powerful orbs of unknown origin, which contain "
"strange entities, who gluttonously drain magical energy from the air, making "
"spells cast into the area in reach of the orb pretty much useless. Such orbs "
"also give their bearers some of their absorbed power (to heal the bearer's "
"wounds, focusing some of the orb's collected energy onto enemies in a beam, "
"as well as enchanting their weapon with life-draining properties) in "
"exchange for the matriarchs carrying them to locations that haven't been "
